    <h1>Hashtag</h1>
    <p class="description">The <strong>#</strong> symbol followed by a keyword that categorises social media content. Posts with at least one hashtag receive <strong>12.6% more engagement</strong> than posts without, per Later's analysis of 18 million Instagram posts.</p>
    <div class="post-meta">
      <div class="meta-author">
